#. <section class="sutta" id="sn55.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn55.10:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 55"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Veḷudvāravagga"
msgstr "1. At Bamboo Gate"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn55.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Tatiyagiñjakāvasathasutta"
msgstr "10. At the Brick Hall (3rd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.10:1.1"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Ānanda said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn55.10:1.2"
msgid "“kakkaṭo nāma, bhante, ñātike upāsako kālaṅkato;"
msgstr "“Sir, the layman named Kakkaṭa has passed away in Nādika."

msgctxt "sn55.10:1.3"
msgid "tassa kā gati, ko abhisamparāyo?"
msgstr "Where has he been reborn in his next life?"

msgctxt "sn55.10:1.4"
msgid "Kaḷibho nāma, bhante, ñātike upāsako … pe …"
msgstr "The laymen named Kaḷibha,"

msgctxt "sn55.10:1.5"
msgid "nikato nāma, bhante, ñātike upāsako …"
msgstr "Nikata,"

msgctxt "sn55.10:1.6"
msgid "kaṭissaho nāma, bhante, ñātike upāsako …"
msgstr "Kaṭissaha,"

msgctxt "sn55.10:1.7"
msgid "tuṭṭho nāma, bhante, ñātike upāsako …"
msgstr "Tuṭṭha,"

msgctxt "sn55.10:1.8"
msgid "santuṭṭho nāma, bhante, ñātike upāsako …"
msgstr "Santuṭṭha,"

msgctxt "sn55.10:1.9"
msgid "bhaddo nāma, bhante, ñātike upāsako …"
msgstr "Bhadda, and"

msgctxt "sn55.10:1.10"
msgid "subhaddo nāma, bhante, ñātike upāsako kālaṅkato;"
msgstr "Subhadda have passed away in Nādika."

msgctxt "sn55.10:1.11"
msgid "tassa kā gati ko abhisamparāyo”ti?"
msgstr "Where have they been reborn in the next life?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.359"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.10:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Kakkaṭo, ānanda, upāsako kālaṅkato pañcannaṃ orambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ "
"parikkhayā opapātiko tattha parinibbāyī anāvattidhammo tasmā lokā."
msgstr "“Ānanda, the laymen Kakkaṭa,"

msgctxt "sn55.10:2.2"
msgid "Kaḷibho, ānanda … pe …"
msgstr "Kaḷibha,"

msgctxt "sn55.10:2.3"
msgid "nikato, ānanda …"
msgstr "Nikata,"

msgctxt "sn55.10:2.4"
msgid "kaṭissaho, ānanda …"
msgstr "Kaṭissaha,"

msgctxt "sn55.10:2.5"
msgid "tuṭṭho, ānanda …"
msgstr "Tuṭṭha,"

msgctxt "sn55.10:2.6"
msgid "santuṭṭho, ānanda …"
msgstr "Santuṭṭha,"

msgctxt "sn55.10:2.7"
msgid "bhaddo, ānanda … pe …"
msgstr "Bhadda,"

msgctxt "sn55.10:2.8"
msgid ""
"subhaddo, ānanda, upāsako kālaṅkato pañcannaṃ orambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ "
"parikkhayā opapātiko tattha parinibbāyī anāvattidhammo tasmā lokā."
msgstr ""
"and Subhadda passed away having ended the five lower fetters. They’ve been "
"reborn spontaneously, and will be extinguished there, not liable to return "
"from that world."

msgctxt "sn55.10:2.9"
msgid "(Sabbe ekagatikā kātabbā.)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.10:3.1"
msgid ""
"Paropaññāsa, ānanda, ñātike upāsakā kālaṅkatā pañcannaṃ orambhāgiyānaṃ "
"saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā opapātikā tattha parinibbāyino anāvattidhammā tasmā "
"lokā."
msgstr ""
"Over fifty laymen in Nādika have passed away having ended the five lower "
"fetters. They’ve been reborn spontaneously, and will be extinguished there, "
"not liable to return from that world."

msgctxt "sn55.10:3.2"
msgid ""
"Sādhikanavuti, ānanda, ñātike upāsakā kālaṅkatā tiṇṇaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ "
"parikkhayā rāgadosamohānaṃ tanuttā sakadāgāmino; sakideva imaṃ lokaṃ āgantvā "
"dukkhassantaṃ karissanti."
msgstr ""
"More than ninety laymen in Nādika have passed away having ended three "
"fetters, and weakened greed, hate, and delusion. They’re once-returners, who "
"will come back to this world once only, then make an end of suffering."

msgctxt "sn55.10:3.3"
msgid ""
"Chātirekāni kho, ānanda, pañcasatāni ñātike upāsakā kālaṅkatā tiṇṇaṃ "
"saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā sotāpannā avinipātadhammā niyatā sambodhiparāyaṇā."
msgstr ""
"In excess of five hundred laymen in Nādika have passed away having ended "
"three fetters. They’re stream-enterers, not liable to be reborn in the "
"underworld, bound for awakening."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.10:4.1"
msgid "Anacchariyaṃ kho panetaṃ, ānanda, yaṃ manussabhūto kālaṃ kareyya;"
msgstr "It’s hardly surprising that a human being should pass away."

msgctxt "sn55.10:4.2"
msgid ""
"tasmiṃ tasmiñce maṃ kālaṅkate upasaṅkamitvā etamatthaṃ paṭipucchissatha. "
"Vihesā pesā, ānanda, assa tathāgatassa."
msgstr ""
"But if you should come and ask me about it each and every time someone "
"passes away, that would be a bother for me."

msgctxt "sn55.10:4.3"
msgid ""
"Tasmātihānanda, dhammādāsaṃ nāma dhammapariyāyaṃ desessāmi; yena samannāgato "
"ariyasāvako ākaṅkhamāno attanāva attānaṃ byākareyya:"
msgstr ""
"So Ānanda, I will teach you the explanation of the Dhamma called ‘the mirror "
"of the teaching’. A noble disciple who has this may declare of themselves:"

msgctxt "sn55.10:4.4"
msgid ""
"‘khīṇanirayomhi khīṇatiracchānayoni khīṇapettivisayo "
"khīṇāpāyaduggativinipāto, sotāpannohamasmi avinipātadhammo niyato "
"sambodhiparāyaṇo’."
msgstr ""
"‘I’ve finished with rebirth in hell, the animal realm, and the ghost realm. "
"I’ve finished with all places of loss, bad places, the underworld. I am a "
"stream-enterer! I’m not liable to be reborn in the underworld, and am bound "
"for awakening.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.10:5.1"
msgid ""
"Katamo ca so, ānanda, dhammādāso dhammapariyāyo; yena samannāgato "
"ariyasāvako ākaṅkhamāno attanāva attānaṃ byākareyya:"
msgstr "And what is that mirror of the teaching?"

msgctxt "sn55.10:5.2"
msgid ""
"‘khīṇanirayomhi khīṇatiracchānayoni khīṇapettivisayo "
"khīṇāpāyaduggativinipāto, sotāpannohamasmi avinipātadhammo niyato "
"sambodhiparāyaṇo’."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.360"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.10:6.1"
msgid ""
"Idhānanda, ariyasāvako buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti—itipi so "
"bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti."
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple has experiential confidence in the Buddha …"

msgctxt "sn55.10:6.2"
msgid "Dhamme … pe …"
msgstr "the teaching …"

msgctxt "sn55.10:6.3"
msgid "saṅghe … pe …"
msgstr "the Saṅgha …"

msgctxt "sn55.10:6.4"
msgid ""
"ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgato hoti akhaṇḍehi … pe … samādhisaṃvattanikehi."
msgstr ""
"And they have the ethical conduct loved by the noble ones … leading to "
"immersion."

msgctxt "sn55.10:6.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho so, ānanda, dhammādāso dhammapariyāyo;"
msgstr "This is that mirror of the teaching."

msgctxt "sn55.10:6.6"
msgid "yena samannāgato ariyasāvako ākaṅkhamāno attanāva attānaṃ byākareyya:"
msgstr "A noble disciple who has this may declare of themselves:"

msgctxt "sn55.10:6.7"
msgid ""
"‘khīṇanirayomhi khīṇatiracchānayoni khīṇapettivisayo "
"khīṇāpāyaduggativinipāto, sotāpannohamasmi avinipātadhammo niyato "
"sambodhiparāyaṇo’”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I’ve finished with rebirth in hell, the animal realm, and the ghost realm. "
"I’ve finished with all places of loss, bad places, the underworld. I am a "
"stream-enterer! I’m not liable to be reborn in the underworld, and am bound "
"for awakening.’”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.10:6.8"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.10:6.9"
msgid "Veḷudvāravaggo paṭhamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.10:7.1"
msgid "Rājā ogadhadīghāvu,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn55.10:7.2"
msgid "sāriputtāpare duve;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn55.10:7.3"
msgid "Thapatī veḷudvāreyyā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn55.10:7.4"
msgid "giñjakāvasathe tayoti."
msgstr ""
